<%# Minimal document wrapper for the reimbursements Notifier emails (sent via
    Graph, not ActionMailer — see Reimbursements::Notifier#send_email). These
    are short, plain finance notices; the app's shared shared/mail/_header +
    _footer layout is a full Bedlam-branded marketing template (social icons,
    unsubscribe copy) that would be the wrong tone here, so this is its own,
    deliberately bare layout rather than reusing that one. %>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
<title><%= @subject %></title>
<!--[if mso]>
<style type="text/css">
table, td { font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; }
</style>
<![endif]-->
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
<%= yield %>
</body>
</html>
